OL,3,CLive facial recognition: Why is Asda's
OL,4,Ctrial of the technology causing a stir?
OL,6,FThe two-month trial will see the faces
OL,7,Fof shoppers scanned and compared to a
OL,8,Fdatabase of "individuals who have
OL,9,Fpreviously committed criminal activity
OL,10,Fon an Asda site".
OL,12,FIf a match is found, Asda's head
OL,13,Foffice security team will alert the
OL,14,Fstore. The five stores involved in the
OL,15,Ftrial are all in Greater Manchester:
OL,16,FAshton, Chadderton, Eastlands,
OL,17,FHarpurhey and Trafford Park.
