OL,3,CLive facial recognition: Why is Asda's
OL,4,Ctrial of the technology causing a stir?
OL,6,FThe supermarket giant said it's in
OL,7,Fresponse to a rise in retail crime,
OL,8,Fwith more than 1,400 assaults on staff
OL,9,Fin Asda stores recorded last year - an
OL,10,Faverage of four per day.
OL,12,FLiz Evans, Chief Commercial Officer at
OL,13,FAsda, said: "We consistently look for
OL,14,Fnew ways to improve the security in
OL,15,Four stores and this trial will help us
OL,16,Funderstand if facial recognition
OL,17,Ftechnology can reduce the number of
OL,18,Fincidents and provide greater
OL,19,Fprotection to everybody in our stores."
