OL,3,CLive facial recognition: Why is Asda's
OL,4,Ctrial of the technology causing a stir?
OL,6,FBut some have claimed the trial
OL,7,Famounts to an infringement of privacy
OL,8,Fand data protection, with the hashtag
OL,9,F_StopAsdaSpying trending on social
OL,10,Fmedia platform X.
OL,12,FCampaign group Big Brother Watch has
OL,13,Furged Asda to abandon the trial.
OL,15,FThe organisation's Senior Advocacy
OL,16,FOfficer Madeleine Stone said: "Asda is
OL,17,Fadding customers to secret watchlists
OL,18,Fwith no due process, meaning people
OL,19,Fcould be blacklisted despite being
OL,20,Finnocent.
