OL,3,CLive facial recognition: Why is Asda's
OL,4,Ctrial of the technology causing a stir?
OL,6,FLive facial recognition has been used
OL,7,Fby six police forces in the UK since
OL,8,Ftrials were conducted in 2018. Last
OL,9,Fyear, ITV News spent time with the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police, who said they
OL,11,Fdeployed the technology 160 times in
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FOther supermarkets have also used the
OL,15,Ftech, including convenience chain
OL,16,FSouthern Co-op, which deploys it in
OL,17,Fsome of its branches.
