OL,3,CLive facial recognition: Why is Asda's
OL,4,Ctrial of the technology causing a stir?
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Asda said: "Like
OL,7,Fall retailers, our stores are subject
OL,8,Fto increasing and unacceptable levels
OL,9,Fof retail crime.
OL,11,F"We have launched this trial in five
OL,12,Fstores for a limited period to assess
OL,13,Fhow it can keep colleagues and
OL,14,Fcustomers safe. This trial uses Asda's
OL,15,Fexisting CCTV system and fully
OL,16,Fcomplies with all data protection
OL,17,Fregulations."
